| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3038 — Recovery Inhibition (interlock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6b91a750-7c0a-5cf6-9014-6ee8b26a9a00"
